Package: CEPALSTATr
Type: Package
Title: An R package to search and download data from CEPALSTAT WEB SERVICES
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Henry Antonio Osorto Ruiz
Maintainer: Henry Osorto <henryantonioosortoruiz@gmail.com>
Description: The CEPALSTATr package provides access to the statistical information available in CEPALSTAT's integrated databases (data and metadata), joining both data sets to provide a structured database composed of values and their respective labels.
    When consulting an indicator, information is obtained at different levels of disaggregation (country, sex) for specific indicators; the names of variables and labels can be consulted in English or Spanish.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/Henry-Osorto/CEPALSTATr
Encoding: UTF-8
Language: en-US, es
LazyData: true
Imports: xml2, dplyr
